# Specs and Documentation

## Before changing runtime behavior

1. Read relevant spec in `doc/` (index: @doc/README.md)
2. Check implementation map in `docs/architecture/` for v0.2 components
3. Align with ADRs: @doc/20-adr-typescript-nest-langchain.md, @doc/09-adr-reactive-loop.md

## `tasks-clickup/`

Future pipeline specs (ClickUp, GitHub PR, BM25 memory, correlation). **Do not** merge into MVP runtime without explicit intent — many services are not implemented yet.

## When updating docs

- Runtime law changes → update `doc/README.md` and affected numbered specs
- New tool/action → update @doc/14-action-catalog.md if public contract changes
- Release milestones → add note under `doc/release-notes/`

## Prefer references over duplication

In rules and memory files, link to spec paths instead of copying full contracts (keeps docs single source of truth).
